cs.LG, cs.SP, cs.IT, cs.SI, cs.NE 

The paper proposes sparsity-aware data-selective adaptive filtering algorithms with adjustable penalties, which involves optimization and signal processing techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.SP (Signal Processing), cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.SI (Systems and Control), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
